Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord0.25\an8\pos(620,148)\c&H151618&}Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Iska, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... I have difficulty sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's not much\NI often get to do for you as a captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always try to be there\Nif my team needs to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you had that look on your face\Nlike something was off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, spill your guts to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle that ended in a tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it left an emotional scar inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like trauma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... After going through a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you could be psychologically hurt\Nfrom your injury and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After fighting against the Ice Calamity Witch,\Nit's not at all surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I wonder what you can do to fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When something's bothering me, barbeque\Nand a good night's sleep perks me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'm up for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A change in scenery would actually be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little messy, but come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stuffed animal collection has grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? They're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, that's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I shouldn't be seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, nothing good will come out\Nof being cooped up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need is to go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A ticket to the opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a play called {\i1}Tragic Love{\i0}\N{\i1}of Female Knight Beatrix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They perform it in the Neutral city every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this opera, so I bought season\Ntickets and have used 9 out of 10,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but you take the last one, Iska!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But when would I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the next mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is captain's order, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Never let go of them. Those swords\Nare our only hope of restoring this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Iska, we're almost in Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were fast asleep\Nno matter how much I talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I\Nhad a dream about Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about me and Jhin going\Nthrough some intense training...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,More like a nightmare, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't dreamt about\NMaster Cro in forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because I haven't used\Nmy astral swords in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Beatrix. I cannot be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Azel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When we meet again, it will not be in\Na church like tonight, but on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Azel, you're such an idiot... How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhh, please keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the girl in front of me\Nis easily moved to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't focus on the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, why don't you take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I apologize for getting\Nyour handkerchief wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a cheap handker--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you follow me here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, we'll finish this once and--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice! You must not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Neutral city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Any conflict in this city\Nis strictly prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I attack him now, all Neutral cities\Nwould turn against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe I was\Nsitting in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I felt unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were so focused on the play,\Ncrying your eyes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Th-This is just sweat from my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You will forget what you saw here today! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice, you'll draw attention\Nif you raise your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine. We will retreat for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day, Iska.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think, Rin!\NIt was just a force of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my heart was going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the words right out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid you were going to start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not following us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. That swordsman did not take\Na step until we left the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe he sat right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have considered the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about this\Nand go have our meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be\Na famous pasta place around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but all the tables are taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind sharing\Na booked table with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can seat you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's my--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The water went down the wrong pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you ambush us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the closest restaurant\Nto the opera house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And a popular one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I had a reservation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Lady Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't let your guard down, Rin.\NStay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize I'm right here\Nand I can hear you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be in the Neutral city, but to dine\Ntogether with an Imperial soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll look like I ran away scared\Nif I leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's eat--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, sorry, that was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, you may go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You reached out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Salmon and zucchini pasta with heavy cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooked {\i1}ben cotta{\i0} and light on the pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have tea with one sugar cube\Nafter the meal, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you two are in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know each--?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like pasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else would I be talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. It's probably my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it with a creamy sauce like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's also good with a dash of ground pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple yet delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it's this hot outside,\Ncold pasta is another good option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Cold pasta is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see cherry tomatoes at the market,\NI always make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Cold tomato pasta is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I could eat it all summer--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've stopped eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I interrupted your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, pasta should always be cooked to al dente.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Such amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ben cotta{\i0} is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep today's events\Nto yourself, Lady Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I should be reporting this\Nto Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not have fought, but we still\Ncame across an enemy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the enemy's personal item.\NNo reason to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That swordsman is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He may become your biggest obstacle one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rin, you're to blame, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you made a comment about pasta\Nhaving to be cooked to al dente,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Iska and I kind of formed this weird alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely stated a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Al dente is pasta at its very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No one should deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So hardheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why is it so hard to fall asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Water... I need water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So drink some. This training requires us\Nto run the distance while hydrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I already drank all of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jhin, let me just get a sip of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll bloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jhin, you're such a meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, it's just you, Risya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Issy, Nens, Jhin-Jhin! It's been a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Risya, you're the Special Defense for\NHumankind HQ's special counsel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of trouble\Nhave you brought for us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mismis' unit will be under\Nmy command for this next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What, don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... you're too smart, Risya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'll understand\Nyour strategies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I reviewed your reports\Nof the engagement in Nelka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell everyone's intuitions\Nare still sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I heard you're\Nhaving trouble sleeping, Issy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you not able to enjoy the opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it was great. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragic love stories like that\Nare good from time to time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Risya says it's boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the type of person who\Ndoesn't understand art and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of... Issy, you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Salil Viblanc's art exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won this from a subordinate in a game,\Nbut I don't care for these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So take it, Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ein, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for being late, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, the other day, you mentioned\Nyou fought against an Imperial swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That he was as strong as the Saint Disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Saint Disciples protect the Emperor\Nand are the strongest in the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are saying he is on par with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the Founder fought against tens of\Nthousands of Imperial Army soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Founder had a younger twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was none other than Nebulis I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal bloodline starts with her.\NShe is our ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Empire never knew\Nthat the "Grand Witch,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as they fearfully called her, had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, they rejoiced over the "Grand Witch's"\Ndeath when Nebulis I passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The bind on the Founder is weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw this change in the Founder when,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, you fought against the swordsman\Nof the Empire in the Nelka forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Astral power reacts when its host is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, when the Imperial Army\Nreached the Sovereignty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there were many recordings of\Nastral powers reacting at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true for the Founder's astral power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a sign of her awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, does anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Many mysteries remain in regard\Nto the Founder's astral power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have the Astral Institution\Nquickly look into this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, you shall refrain\Nfrom going to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least until we know who\Nthis Imperial swordsman is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to not overthink things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been having trouble sleeping,\Nso I need a change in scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the Neutral city again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like the other day happens again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a coincidence.\NTo be safe, I won't go to the opera this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I should actually enjoy my break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the art exhibit we're going to is the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would an Imperial soldier\Ncome to Neutral city this often?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to your duty\Nto protect the Empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just point out that Viblanc is\Nan impressionist artist of the Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it isn't weird for me\Nto come see his art.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But should {\i1}you{\i0} be enjoying the art\Nof an Imperial artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Art has no borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the art museum is this way.\NShould we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because it's the city of art
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean they just have\Nto clean up the main streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin... Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?! You're supposed\Nto be at the art museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I already saw most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't see you around,\Nso I thought maybe you got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the princess of the Nebulis Sovereignty,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're a swordsman of the Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured you might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to hide it from you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, my point is we're enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's inappropriate\Nto go to the art museum together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're enemies, but art has no borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were your words, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Iska.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you like this artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The paint right here is a little raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think he paused when he tried\Nto add paint with a painting knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, he repainted it with\Na completely different shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me wonder if the image in his head\Nchanges while he's painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Needing to paint in stronger colors,\Nwith more passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This artist, Viblanc, only paints landscapes.\NCities, streets, boating docks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And he never draws people in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The subject he draws is inorganic\Nand his colors are dark, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very passionate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I can see his personality\Nthrough his art,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think that's what I like about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. I feel the same--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for showing me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to owe you. Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I don't have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how old are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're enemies, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I... If I wanted to,\Nin your current state, I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(548,220,586,354)\b0\pos(640,275)\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\t(0,500,\clip(548,220,742,324))}Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b0\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\pos(632,393)\c&HFEFEFE&\\clip(360,354,410,450)\t(0,830,\clip(360,354,908,412))}The Enemy You and I Met Was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all for today's deliberation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We will reinstate the Successor of the\NBlack Steel, Iska, back to Saint Disciple
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,under the condition that he captures\Nthe Ice Calamity Witch.